<h1 class="xl:text-4xl lg:text-3xl md:text-2xl text-xl font-bold">Cookie Policy</h1>

<p class="text-base text-gray-300">
  We use cookies and similar technologies to help personalize content, tailor your experience, and help us understand how you use our services. By continuing to use our site, you consent to the use of these technologies.
</p>

<section class="space-y-4">
  <h2 class="xl:text-2xl lg:text-xl md:text-lg text-base font-semibold">What are cookies?</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">
    Cookies are small data files stored on your device that help websites remember information about your visit. This can make your next visit easier and the site more useful to you.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="space-y-4">
  <h2 class="xl:text-2xl lg:text-xl md:text-lg text-base font-semibold">How we use cookies</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">
    <li>To remember your preferences and settings.</li>
    <li>To keep you logged in during your visit.</li>
    <li>To analyze traffic and usage patterns.</li>
    <li>To improve the overall user experience.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="space-y-4">
  <h2 class="xl:text-2xl lg:text-xl md:text-lg text-base font-semibold">Your choices</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">
    Most browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. You can choose to block cookies or alert you when cookies are being sent. However, some site features may not function properly without them.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="space-y-4">
  <h2 class="xl:text-2xl lg:text-xl md:text-lg text-base font-semibold">Updates to this policy</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">
    We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. If we make significant changes, we will let you know through the site or via email if applicable.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: August 1, 2025</p>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="mb-2 font-semibold">
    Opt out non-system cookies
  </div>
